public abstract class DatalogSegment
extends List

A DatalogSegment is an abstract classs that is differentiated from List by having a name. This class does not override any of the methods defined in the List class. Overriding will be done in the specializations.

name

protected java.lang.String name
Every DatalogSegment has one of the following four names: Schemes, Facts, Rules, or Queries. The name is set when the specialization is cretaed. This name is used for printing purposes.
